---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import TwoColumnLayout from "../layouts/TwoColumnLayout.astro";
import Ornament from "../components/Ornament.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About">
  <TwoColumnLayout>
    <article>
      <h1>About Chris Busse</h1>
      <p class="meta-text">Technology Leader · Speaker · Writer</p>
      <p>
        I use creativity to guide business, product, and technology leaders through
        complex high-risk enterprise change journeys.
      </p>
      <p>
        For over thirty years, that work has taken many forms. Today it means leading
        Enterprise Client Solutions and AI at SingleStone, where I help consulting
        clients navigate architecture modernization, AI strategy, and domain-driven
        design. I also founded Eszett, where I help artists who reject AI in their
        art leverage it to better position and sell their work.
      </p>
      <Ornament glyph="☙" />
      <p>
        Before that I served as Chief Digital Officer and VP of Delivery at Terazo,
        where I built the firm's Twilio practice and spoke at SIGNAL four times.
        Earlier, I co-founded APIvista, an API strategy consultancy, and delivered
        a keynote at the Nordic APIs Platform Summit in Stockholm. At Capital One,
        I led the launch of DevExchange&mdash;the first public API platform from a
        North American bank&mdash;and founded the API Craft RVA meetup.
      </p>
      <p>
        I've spoken at SXSW Interactive, Nordic APIs, Twilio SIGNAL, APIStrat, and
        dozens of other events over the past fifteen years. My talks explore enterprise
        modernization, API strategy, developer experience, and AI transformation.
      </p>
      <p>
        Based in Richmond, Virginia.
      </p>
    </article>
  </TwoColumnLayout>
</BaseLayout>
